What happens when you lose your soulmate. And how long until you give life another chance? *Pair* is a comedic animated short film by Hoef Entertainment with a serious undertone. Hoef Entertainment published this animated short in 2023 to test a new 3D shading technique. Pair got accepted into multiple short film festivals and competitions.
